sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/System
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Admission Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>Controller
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>GCS:6379/Dashboard:8265
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Pods
    participant JobPod as Submitter Job Pod
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate RayCluster<br/>mTLS (K8s API server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response
    K8sAPI->>Operator: RayCluster Event<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Services<br/>ServiceAccount token
    RayWorker->>RayHead: Register to GCS<br/>6379/TCP (Optional Redis password)
    Prometheus->>Operator: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP (no auth)

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: RayJob Submission
    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create K8s Job (submitter)<br/>ServiceAccount token
    JobPod->>RayHead: Submit job via Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (Optional token)
    JobPod->>RayHead: Poll job status<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (Optional token)
    RayHead-->>JobPod: Job completion status

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: RayService Zero-Downtime Update
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster v1<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>RayHead: Deploy Serve apps<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (Optional token)
    User->>RayHead: Inference requests<br/>8000/TCP HTTP (via Service)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster v2<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>RayHead: Health check v2 Serve<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Service selector to v2<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Delete RayCluster v1<br/>ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 4: Autoscaling
    RayHead->>RayHead: Autoscaler checks GCS<br/>6379/TCP
    RayHead->>K8sAPI: List worker Pods<br/>443/TCP HTTPS (Ray SA token)
    RayHead->>K8sAPI: Create/Delete worker Pods<br/>443/TCP HTTPS (Ray SA token)
    RayWorker->>RayHead: New worker registers to GCS<br/>6379/TCP
